xyz.swatt.data_mapping

Class BigDecimalMapping

  • java.lang.Object
    • xyz.swatt.data_mapping.BigDecimalMapping
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataMapping

    @LogMethods
public class BigDecimalMapping
extends Object
implements DataMapping

    Use this class to validate that 2 different BigDecimals, Doubles, or Floats are equivalent.

    Note: This class is used instead of direct comparison, to simplify large batches of comparisons, and to provide common functionality.

    Author:
    Brandon Dudek (BrandonDudek)
